taly":"意大利坎帕尼亞艾維利努阿利亞諾 易爾皮諾","Italy":"意大利","lifeSummary":"当Guillaume de Sabran于1294年出生在意大利坎帕尼亞艾維利努阿利亞諾 易爾皮諾时，他的父亲Guillaume de Sabran44岁，母亲Rose DE SALMAND44岁。他于1322年6月20日与Contessa Francesca di Celano of Ariano在意大利结婚。他们至少是1个儿子和1个女儿的父母。他去世于1353年10月8日在勒尼 迪 拿坡里享年59岁。"},"hr":{"1294–8 October 1353":"1294.–8. listopada 1353.","1294–1353":"1294.–1353","1310–1379":"1310–1379","1322–1379":"1322.–1379","–1383":"–1383","1250–Male":"1250–preminuo","1250–1329":"1250–1329","19 octobre 1329":"19. listopada 1329.","1379":"1379","1322":"1322.","1310":"1310","1353":"1353","20 June 1322":"20. lipnja 1322.","1383":"1383","1294":"1294.","1250":"1250","1293":"1293.","8 October 1353":"8. listopada 1353.","1329":"1329","Kingdom of Naples":"Regno di Napoli","Les Baux-de-Provence, Bouches-du-Rhône, France":"Les Baux-de-Provence, Bouches-du-Rhône, Francuska","Ariano Irpino, Avellino, Campania, Italy":"Ariano Irpino, Avellino, Campania, Italija","Italy":"Italija"},"cs":{"1294–8 October 1353":"1294–8. října 1353","1294–1353":"1294–1353","1310–1379":"1310–1379","1322–1379":"1322–1379","–1383":"–1383","1250–Male":"1250–Zesnulý","1250–1329":"1250–1329","19 octobre 1329":"19. října 1329","1379":"1379","1322":"1322","1310":"1310","1353":"1353","20 June 1322":"20. června 1322","1383":"1383","1294":"1294","1250":"1250","1293":"1293","8 October 1353":"8. října 1353","1329":"1329","Kingdom of Naples":"Regno di Napoli","Les Baux-de-Provence, Bouches-du-Rhône, France":"Les Baux-de-Provence, Bouches-du-Rhône, Francie","Ariano Irpino, Avellino, Campania, Italy":"Ariano Irpino, Avellino, Campania, Itálie","Italy":"Itálie"},"da":{"1294–8 October 1353":"1294–8. oktober 1353","1294–1353":"1294–1353","1310–1379":"1310–1379","1322–1379":"1322–1379","–1383":"–1383","1250–Male":"1250–Afdød","1250–1329":"1250–1329","19 octobre 1329":"19. oktober 1329","1379":"1379","1322":"1322","1310":"1310","1353":"1353","20 June 1322":"20. juni 1322","1383":"1383","1294":"1294","1250":"1250","1293":"1293","8 October 1353":"8. oktob